COMMENT ON TABLE oats_alr_appl_decisions IS 'An ALR APPL DECISION is a resolution passed by the Commissioner''s of the Agricultural Land Commission pertaining to the inclusion or exclusion of land or permitted land uses within the Agricultural Land Reserve. The Agricultural Land Commission staff makes recommendations to the Commissioners.  Only Commissioners are able to pass resolutions.';

